Wong Lai Cheng, 47, passed away in a fatal accident on Jan. 12 along Pioneer Road North when a private bus mounted the curb and hit her. The bus ended up hitting other vehicles after crossing several lanes.

Videos of the accident have been shared widely and the media covered the incident extensively.

Chua Hanyi, the daughter of the victim, posted on Facebook wishing to clarify “certain details that have been falsely reported and have caused much hurt to my father and I.”
